Uses of Package
org.openwms.core.uaa

  • Packages that use org.openwms.core.uaa 
    Package Description
    org.openwms.core.search
    Definition and implementations of the action search feature.
    org.openwms.core.uaa
    Service definitions and implementations around User Authentication and Authorization (UAA).
    org.openwms.core.uaa.api
    Public RESTful API to User Authentication and Authorization (UAA).
  • Classes in org.openwms.core.uaa used by org.openwms.core.search 
    Class and Description
    User
    An User represents a human user of the system.
  • Classes in org.openwms.core.uaa used by org.openwms.core.uaa 
    Class and Description
    Grant
    A Grant gives permission to access some kind of application object.
    Role
    A Role is a group of Users.
    Role.Builder
    A builder class to construct Role instances.
    SecurityObject
    A SecurityObject is the generalization of Roles and Grants and combines common used properties of both.
    SecurityService
    A SecurityService defines functionality to handle SecurityObjects, especially Grants.
    SystemUser
    A SystemUser is granted with all privileges and omits all defined security constraints.
    User
    An User represents a human user of the system.
    UserDetails
    Detailed information about an User.
    UserDetails.SEX
    The Users sex.
    UserHolder
    An UserHolder exposes an User instance to it's clients.
    UserPassword
    Is a representation of an User together with her password.
    UserWrapper
    An UserWrapper is used as an adapter between Roles, SecurityObjects and Spring's GrantedAuthority objects.
